      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all DIY enthusiasts and restoration lovers! This vehicle is the ultimate project car, offering a fantastic opportunity for someone ready to roll up their sleeves and bring it back to its former glory. While it currently requires significant mechanical repairs and bodywork, it serves as a solid foundation for your next big build. Grab this diamond in the rough and create something truly special!",
